<p begin="00:00:03.036" end="00:00:06.273">&gt;&gt; Jon: JOIN US TOMORROW NIGHT AT 11:00.</p>
<p begin="00:00:06.273" end="00:00:08.342">TOMORROW NIGHT AT 11:00 MATT LONG WILL BE HERE.</p>
<p begin="00:00:08.342" end="00:00:11.845">NEW YORK CITY FIREFIGHTER HIT BY A BUS.</p>
<p begin="00:00:11.845" end="00:00:12.980">HIT BY A BUS.</p>
<p begin="00:00:12.980" end="00:00:15.849">NOW HE&apos;S BACK STRONGER THAN EVER.</p>
