<p begin="00:00:17.818" end="00:00:21.555">AND THE FACT THAT HE IS NOW KICK ALL OF OUR ASSES.</p>
<p begin="00:00:21.555" end="00:00:23.557">IT&apos;S SOMEWHAT OF A REMARKABLE JOURNEY.</p>
<p begin="00:00:23.557" end="00:00:24.458">ANYWAY THAT&apos;S TOMORROW NIGHT.</p>
<p begin="00:00:24.458" end="00:00:25.726">HERE IT IS YOUR MOMENT OF ZEN.</p>
